li></ul></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; tham quan theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng Vi&#7879;t vui v&#7867; nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh su&#7889;t chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">B&#7843;o hi&#7875;m v&#7899;i m&#7913;c b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a 100.000.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p. Kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho kh&aacute;ch t&#7915; 80 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng: n&oacute;n du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t, n&#432;&#7899;c, kh&#259;n l&#7841;nh.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Bia hay n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t trong c&aacute;c b&#7919;a &#259;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tham quan ngo&agrave;i ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, gi&#7863;t &#7911;i&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; c&aacute;p treo &#273;i B&agrave; N&agrave;, c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n Ch&acirc;u &Aacute;,</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">01 b&#7919;a tr&#432;a ng&agrave;y th&#7913; 5 theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; b&atilde;i bi&#7875;n: d&ugrave;, v&otilde;ng, t&#7855;m n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Thu&#7871; VAT.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-calendar-check-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;c</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div id=\"mda-table-price\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"mda-list-price mda-tap ative table-responsive mCustomScrollbar _mCS_1 mCS_no_scrollbar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 504.375px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; touch-action: auto;\"><div id=\"mCSB_1\" class=\"mCustomScrollBox mCS-light mCSB_horizontal mCSB_inside\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; height: 58px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; direction: ltr; max-height: none;\"><div id=\"mCSB_1_container\" class=\"mCSB_container mCS_x_hidden mCS_no_scrollbar_x\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; width: 773.328px; height: auto; position: relative; top: 0px; left: 0px;\"><table class=\"table\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 773px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-spacing: 0px;\"><thead class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><tr class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><th class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857;\">STT</th><th width=\"85\" class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857; white-space: nowrap;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh</th><th class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857;\">&#272;&#7863;c &#273;i&#7875;m</th><th width=\"100px\" class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857;\">Gi&aacute; t&#7915;</th><th width=\"90px\" class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857;\">S&#7889; Ch&#7895;</th><th width=\"125px\" class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); line-height: 1.42857;\">Book tour</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"responsive\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-sticky-note-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ghi ch&uacute;</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Gi&#7901; bay c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng. Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; thay &#273;&#7893;i ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh cho ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i gi&#7901; bay m&#7899;i nh&#432;ng s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m v&#7873; c&aacute;c kho&#7843;n chi ph&iacute; ph&aacute;t sinh.</em></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; ve&#769; da&#768;nh cho tre&#777; em:</span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></u></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 02 tu&#7893;i: mi&#7877;n gi&aacute; tour, gi&aacute; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, Cha, M&#7865; ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n &#273;i k&egrave;m t&#7921; lo c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; &#259;n, ng&#7911;, tham quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) cho b&eacute;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 02 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 05 tu&#7893;i: 90% gi&aacute; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay; mi&#7877;n gi&aacute; tour. Cha, M&#7865; ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n &#273;i k&egrave;m t&#7921; lo c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; &#259;n, ng&#7911;, tham quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) cho b&eacute;. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 5 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i mua &frac12; v&eacute; tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 05 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 11 tu&#7893;i: 90% gi&aacute; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay; 50% gi&aacute; tour. Bao g&#7891;m c&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#259;n u&#7889;ng, gh&#7871; ng&#7891;i tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng&#7911; chung v&#7899;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 5 &#273;&#7871;n d&#432;&#7899;i 11 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n Cha, M&#7865; n&ecirc;n mua th&ecirc;m 1 su&#7845;t gi&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#417;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">T&#7915; 11 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n: 100% gi&aacute; tour v&agrave; ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n nh&#432; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Quy &#273;&#7883;nh thanh to&aacute;n, h&#7911;y v&eacute;:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Sau khi x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n (&iacute;t nh&#7845;t 50% ti&#7873;n c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895; v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour tr&#432;&#7899;c 15 ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Khi &#273;&#7871;n ng&agrave;y thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour, n&#7871;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&uacute;ng h&#7841;n v&agrave; &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem nh&#432; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; &yacute; hu&#7927; tour v&agrave; m&#7845;t h&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; M&aacute;y Bay / v&eacute; xe l&#7917;a / v&eacute; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu&#7845;t ngay sau khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&oacute;ng ti&#7873;n v&agrave; c&oacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n s&#7921; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c v&#7873; h&#7885;, t&ecirc;n (&#273;&uacute;ng t&#7915;ng k&yacute; t&#7921; ghi trong h&#7897; chi&#7871;u ho&#7863;c CMND), ng&agrave;y-th&aacute;ng-n&#259;m sinh &hellip; c&#7911;a h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n. M&#7885;i s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n v&eacute; &#273;&atilde; xu&#7845;t: ng&agrave;y gi&#7901; &#273;i, t&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch, h&#7911;y v&eacute;, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng ch&#7883;u chi ph&iacute; theo qui &#273;&#7883;nh sau:</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Ngay sau khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour n&#7871;u h&#7911;y s&#7869; b&#7883; ph&#7841;t ti&#7873;n tour v&agrave; v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay:&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c ho&#7863;c thanh to&aacute;n ho&#7863;c tr&#432;&#7899;c 15 ng&agrave;y: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 35% ti&#7873;n tour+ 100% V&eacute; m&aacute;y bay.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 10 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 50% ti&#7873;n tour + 100% v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 70% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp; + 100% v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y&nbsp; 05 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 100% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp; + 100% v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7877; gi&#7901; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh l&agrave; h&#7911;y 5 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Do t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;o&agrave;n gh&eacute;p kh&aacute;ch l&#7867;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; cho &#273;&#7911; &#273;o&agrave;n (10 kh&aacute;ch ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n) th&igrave; &#273;o&agrave;n s&#7869; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&uacute;ng l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;o&agrave;n d&#432;&#7899;i 10 kh&aacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 3 ng&agrave;y v&agrave; s&#7869; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n l&#7841;i ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh m&#7899;i ho&#7863;c ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; to&agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i C&ocirc;ng ty ho&#7863;c qua fax, email, tin nh&#7855;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng ty x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">C&aacute;c ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c, thanh to&aacute;n, hu&#7927; v&agrave; d&#7901;i tour: kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; 7, Ch&#7911; Nh&#7853;t.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Trong nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng nh&#432;: kh&#7911;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;o &#273;&#7897;ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, l&#361; l&#7909;t&hellip; Tu&#7923; theo t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&agrave; s&#7921; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n, an to&agrave;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ty Du L&#7883;ch s&#7869; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i nh&#432; sau: hu&#7927; ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i v&#7899;i chi ph&iacute; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham quan tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh th&igrave; Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; thanh to&aacute;n kho&#7843;n ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;y. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&#7895;i b&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a, gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; b&ecirc;n b&#7883; thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i nh&#7857;m gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&aacute;c t&#7893;n th&#7845;t g&acirc;y ra v&igrave; l&yacute; do b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng.&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh, gi&#7901; bay do l&#7895;i c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, t&agrave;u ho&#7843;, t&agrave;u thu&#7927;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m b&#7845;t k&#7923; ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;o do l&#7895;i tr&ecirc;n nh&#432;: ph&aacute;t sinh b&#7919;a &#259;n, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n di chuy&#7875;n, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n, &hellip;.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">L&#432;u &yacute;:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i g&#7903;i gi&#7845;y t&#7901; t&ugrave;y th&acirc;n cho &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; du l&#7883;ch &#273;&#7875; v&agrave;o t&ecirc;n xu&#7845;t v&eacute; v&agrave; mua b&#7843;o hi&#7875;m du l&#7883;ch. Nh&#7919;ng gi&#7845;y t&#7901; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng (CMND ho&#7863;c Passport) thu&#7897;c v&#7873; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng. M&#7885;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; nh&#432; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh, th&ocirc;ng tin gi&#7845;y t&#7901; trong b&#7843;n g&#7889;c b&#7883; m&#7901;, kh&ocirc;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng; Passport, CMND h&#7871;t h&#7841;n,&hellip; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t Vi&#7879;t Nam, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m v&agrave; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; b&#7845;t c&#7913; chi ph&iacute; ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;o.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i kh&aacute;ch N&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i/Vi&#7879;t Ki&#7873;u: Khi &#273;i tour ph&#7843;i mang theo &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; Passport (H&#7897; Chi&#7871;u), Visa Vi&#7879;t Nam b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh c&ograve;n h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c l&ecirc;n m&aacute;y bay theo qui &#273;&#7883;nh h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em (d&#432;&#7899;i 12 tu&#7893;i) khi &#273;i du l&#7883;ch mang theo gi&#7845;y khai sinh (b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh ho&#7863;c sao y c&oacute; th&#7883; th&#7921;c c&ograve;n h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng) &#273;&#7875;&nbsp; l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7915; 14 tu&#7893;i b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i c&oacute; CMND ho&#7863;c Passport (c&ograve;n h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng), KH&Ocirc;NG S&#7916; D&#7908;NG GI&#7844;Y KHAI SINH. N&#7871;u tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 14 tu&#7893;i ch&#432;a c&oacute; CMND ho&#7863;c Passport b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i c&oacute; Gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n nh&acirc;n th&acirc;n (C&oacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n ch&iacute;nh quy&#7873;n (c&ograve;n h&#7841;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng)) + Gi&#7845;y khai sinh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">M&#7897;t s&#7889; th&#7913; t&#7921;, chi ti&#7871;t trong ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh; gi&#7901; bay; gi&#7901; xe l&#7917;a; gi&#7901; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7875; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a chuy&#7871;n &#273;i (th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t, giao th&ocirc;ng&hellip;)</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qui &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#7853;n &amp; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n/resort: nh&#7853;n ph&ograve;ng sau 14H00 v&agrave; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c 12H00 .</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&agrave;nh l&yacute; v&agrave; t&#432; trang du kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; b&#7843;o qu&#7843;n trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh du l&#7883;ch .</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&igrave; l&yacute; do s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&agrave; an to&agrave;n v&#7879; sinh th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m, Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng kh&ocirc;ng mang th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m t&#7915; b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i v&agrave;o nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i th&#7913;c u&#7889;ng khi mang v&agrave;o ph&#7843;i c&oacute; s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng &yacute; c&#7911;a nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n v&agrave; b&#7883; t&iacute;nh ph&iacute; n&#7871;u c&oacute;</li></ul></div></div></div></body></html>\r\n', '2020-04-29 09:03:04', '2020-06-25 14:16:06', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '6', '0000-00-00', 'Xe Ô Tô', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 3, 11, 4);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`id`, `tour_id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tour_TypeTour_id`, `status`, `check_home_page`, `check_trending`, `best_seller`, `tour_date`, `date_start`, `transport`, `place_start`, `numratings`, `allstar`, `star`) VALUES
(20, '13917', 'Du lịch Miền Tây - Tour Mỹ Tho - Cần Thơ 2 ngày khởi hành từ Sài Gòn', 'du-lich-mien-tay-tour-my-tho-can-tho-2-ngay-khoi-hanh-tu-sai-gon', 1499000, 'upload/images/1593102185_Tour-My-tho-du-lich-viet.jpg', '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><!--?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?--><html><body><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-info-circle\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">&#272;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 773px;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px; width: 154px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">M&#7929; Tho &ndash; Ch&ugrave;a V&#297;nh Tr&agrave;ng - C&#7891;n Long &ndash; L&acirc;n &ndash; Qui &ndash; Ph&#7909;ng - C&#7847;n Th&#417; &ndash; Ch&#7907; n&#7893;i C&aacute;i R&#259;ng</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">2 ng&agrave;y 1 &#273;&ecirc;m</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Th&#7913; 7 h&agrave;ng tu&#7847;n</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">V&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Xe du l&#7883;ch &#273;&#7901;i m&#7899;i</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"http://dulichviet.com.vn/du-lich-mien-tay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Du L&#7883;ch Mi&#7873;n T&acirc;y</a></span>&nbsp;- Xu&ocirc;i theo d&ograve;ng n&#432;&#7899;c du kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i ch&#7907; n&#7893;i C&aacute;i R&#259;ng &#273;&#7875; ch&#7913;ng ki&#7871;n &#273;i&#7873;u k&igrave; l&#7841;, ch&#7907; m&agrave; n&#7893;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng? Du kh&aacute;ch &#273;i ch&#7907; n&#7893;i C&aacute;i R&#259;ng tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng C&#7847;n Th&#417; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7875; ng&#7855;m nh&igrave;n nh&#7919;ng ghe thuy&#7873;n &#273;&#7847;y &#7855;p hoa qu&#7843;, h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a m&agrave; c&ograve;n &#273;&#7875; th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7913;c h&#432;&#417;ng v&#7883; t&ocirc; h&#7911; ti&#7871;u hay t&ocirc; b&uacute;n cua th&#417;m ngon gi&#7919;a d&ograve;ng n&#432;&#7899;c m&ecirc;nh m&ocirc;ng. B&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh tham quan c&aacute;c Ch&#7907; n&#7893;i, du kh&aacute;ch c&ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c&nbsp;vi&#7871;ng th&#259;m Thi&#7873;n Vi&#7879;n Tr&uacute;c L&acirc;m Ph&#432;&#417;ng Nam, Thi&#7873;n Vi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ngh&#7879; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t T&acirc;y &#272;&ocirc; - ng&ocirc;i ch&ugrave;a r&#7897;ng nh&#7845;t khu v&#7921;c &#272;&#7891;ng b&#7857;ng s&ocirc;ng C&#7917;u Long, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&ecirc;n di&#7879;n t&iacute;ch g&#7847;n 4 ha, v&#7899;i k&#7871;t c&#7845;u l&#7907;p ng&oacute;i, khung c&#7897;t g&#7895; lim, ch&aacute;nh &#273;i&#7879;n r&#7897;ng c&ugrave;ng nh&agrave; t&#7893;, nhi&#7873;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Ph&#7853;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&agrave;m b&#7857;ng g&#7895; Du Sam.&nbsp;</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"du l&#7883;ch Mi&#7873;n T&acirc;y\" src=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/images/bandidau/Thi%E1%BB%81n%20Vi%E1%BB%87n%20Tr%C3%BAc%20L%C3%A2m.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 800px; height: 533px;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Trong kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; m&aacute;t m&#7867; &#273;&#7847;u xu&acirc;n, du kh&aacute;ch tham gia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/tour-le-chua-tam-linh\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Tour l&#7877; ch&ugrave;a &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m</span></a>&nbsp;&#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i&nbsp;nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m du l&#7883;ch t&acirc;m linh n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng nh&#432;&nbsp;Thi&#7873;n Vi&#7879;n Tr&uacute;c L&acirc;m, v&#7915;a c&oacute; th&#7875; chi&ecirc;m b&aacute;i c&#7843;nh ch&ugrave;a uy nghi&ecirc;m tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7865;p, v&#7915;a th&#7881;nh c&#7847;u cho gia &#273;&igrave;nh s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e, may m&#7855;n, m&#7897;t n&#259;m m&#7899;i b&igrave;nh an.</em></p></div><div class=\"linkMore text-right\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a id=\"xemthem\" data-id=\"13917\" data-table=\"tour\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Xem th&ecirc;m &raquo;</a></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-map-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"listDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; position: relative;\"><div class=\"day active\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 1 |</span>&nbsp;TP. HCM &ndash; TI&#7872;N GIANG &ndash; M&#7928; THO &ndash; C&#7846;N TH&#416; (&#258;n s&aacute;ng, tr&#432;a, chi&#7873;u)</div><div class=\"contDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">S&aacute;ng:</span>&nbsp;Xe v&agrave; H&#432;&#7899;ng D&#7851;n Vi&ecirc;n C&ocirc;ng Ty Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t &#273;&oacute;n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m h&#7865;n.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;i M&#7929; Tho.&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng b&#7919;a s&aacute;ng t&#7841;i Trung L&#432;&#417;ng. Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c l&#7897; tr&igrave;nh gh&eacute; tham quan ch&ugrave;a V&#297;nh Tr&agrave;ng v&#7899;i l&#7889;i ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u v&agrave; Ch&acirc;u &Aacute;.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;o&agrave;n xu&#7889;ng b&#7871;n &#273;&ograve; 30/04, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch xu&#7889;ng thuy&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng ngo&#7841;n c&#7843;nh s&ocirc;ng n&#432;&#7899;c mi&#7873;n T&acirc;y Nam B&#7897; v&#7899;i 4 c&ugrave; lao: Long, L&acirc;n , Quy, Ph&#7909;ng, th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7913;c h&#432;&#417;ng v&#7883; ng&#7885;t ng&agrave;o c&#7911;a tr&aacute;i d&#7915;a xi&ecirc;m.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Thuy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;a &#273;o&agrave;n &#273;i tham quan c&ugrave; lao Th&#7899;i S&#417;n, &#273;i b&#7897; tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave;ng, tham quan tr&#7841;i nu&ocirc;i ong m&#7853;t, u&#7889;ng tr&agrave; m&#7853;t ong, th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7913;c c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i m&#7913;t &#273;&#7863;c s&#7843;n. Tham quan v&#432;&#7901;n c&acirc;y &#259;n tr&aacute;i, th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7913;c c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i tr&aacute;i c&acirc;y t&#7841;i v&#432;&#7901;n, nghe nh&#7841;c t&agrave;i t&#7917; Nam B&#7897;. &#272;i xu&#7891;ng ch&egrave;o trong r&#7841;ch d&#7915;a n&#432;&#7899;c thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Thuy&#7873;n l&#7899;n &#273;&#432;a kh&aacute;ch sang B&#7871;n Tre tham quan l&ograve; k&#7865;o d&#7915;a n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng B&#7871;n Tre.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tham quan C&#7891;n Ph&#7909;ng ( Di t&iacute;ch &Ocirc;ng &#272;&#7841;o D&#7915;a).</div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Tr&#432;a:</span>&nbsp;D&ugrave;ng c&#417;m tr&#432;a. Thuy&#7873;n &#273;&#432;a du kh&aacute;ch tr&#7903; l&#7841;i B&#7871;n T&agrave;u 30/4, kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;i C&#7847;n Th&#417;.</div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Chi&#7873;u:</span>&nbsp;D&ugrave;ng c&#417;m chi&#7873;u, ngh&#7881; &#273;&ecirc;m kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n t&#7841;i C&#7847;n Th&#417;.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 2 |</span>&nbsp;CH&#7906; N&#7892;I C&Aacute;I R&#258;NG &ndash; THI&#7872;N VI&#7878;N TR&Uacute;C L&Acirc;M &ndash; TP. HCM (&#258;n s&aacute;ng, tr&#432;a)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-paperclip\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">D&#7883;ch v&#7909; bao g&#7891;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; tour bao g&#7891;m:</span></u></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Xe tham quan (xe 16 ch&#7895;, 29 ch&#7895;, 35 ch&#7895;, 45 ch&#7895;) t&ugrave;y theo s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;ch th&#7921;c t&#7871; tr&ecirc;n chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#258;n u&#7889;ng theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh. Bao g&#7891;m 3 b&#7919;a ch&iacute;nh + 2 b&#7919;a &#259;n s&aacute;ng</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng 3*: Ph&#432;&#417;ng &#272;&ocirc;ng, Ninh Ki&#7873;u, H&#7853;u Giang, Holiday, 2 kh&aacute;ch/ph&ograve;ng, n&#7871;u l&#7867; ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7913; 3 ng&#7911; gh&eacute;p ph&ograve;ng 3 ho&#7863;c ph&#7909; ph&iacute; ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; tham quan + t&agrave;u thuy&#7873;n theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng Vi&#7879;t vui v&#7867; nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh su&#7889;t chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">B&#7843;o hi&#7875;m v&#7899;i m&#7913;c b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng 100.000.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p. Kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho kh&aacute;ch t&#7915; 80 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng: n&oacute;n du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t, n&#432;&#7899;c.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m:</span></u></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Bia hay n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t trong c&aacute;c b&#7919;a &#259;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tham quan ngo&agrave;i ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, gi&#7863;t &#7911;i&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ph&#7909; ph&iacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ph&#7909; ph&iacute; ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Thu&#7871; VAT.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-sticky-note-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ghi ch&uacute;</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(&#272;o&agrave;n t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 20 kh&aacute;ch kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh)</em></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; text-align: justify;\"></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; ve&#769; da&#768;nh cho tre&#777; em:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 05 tu&#7893;i: mi&#7877;n gi&aacute; tour. Cha, M&#7865; ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n &#273;i k&egrave;m t&#7921; lo c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; &#259;n, ng&#7911;, tham quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) cho b&eacute;. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 5 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i mua &frac12; v&eacute; tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 05 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 10 tu&#7893;i: 75% gi&aacute; tour. Bao g&#7891;m c&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#259;n u&#7889;ng, gh&#7871; ng&#7891;i tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng&#7911; chung v&#7899;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 5 &#273;&#7871;n d&#432;&#7899;i 10tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n Cha M&#7865; n&ecirc;n mua th&ecirc;m 1 su&#7845;t gi&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#417;n ho&#7863;c v&eacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">T&#7915; 10 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n: 100% gi&aacute; tour v&agrave; ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n nh&#432; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">&#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave; h&#7911;y v&eacute; tour:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Sau khi x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n (&iacute;t nh&#7845;t 50% ti&#7873;n c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895; v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour tr&#432;&#7899;c 10 ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Khi &#273;&#7871;n ng&agrave;y thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour, n&#7871;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&uacute;ng h&#7841;n v&agrave; &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem nh&#432; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; &yacute; hu&#7927; tour v&agrave; m&#7845;t h&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; M&aacute;y Bay / v&eacute; xe l&#7917;a / v&eacute; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu&#7845;t ngay sau khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, thanh to&aacute;n, x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n (h&#7885; t&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng n&#259;m sinh&hellip;) v&agrave; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n v&eacute; nh&#432; sau: Kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7893;i t&ecirc;n, ho&agrave;n v&eacute;, h&#7911;y v&eacute;, thay &#273;&#7893;i ng&agrave;y, thay &#273;&#7893;i h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Ngay sau khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour n&#7871;u h&#7911;y s&#7869; b&#7883; ph&#7841;t ti&#7873;n tour:</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c ho&#7863;c thanh to&aacute;n ho&#7863;c tr&#432;&#7899;c 15 ng&agrave;y: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 10% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 10 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 50% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 70% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y&nbsp; 05 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 100% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i C&ocirc;ng ty ho&#7863;c qua fax, email, tin nh&#7855;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng ty x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Do t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;o&agrave;n gh&eacute;p kh&aacute;ch l&#7867;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; cho &#273;&#7911; &#273;o&agrave;n (20 kh&aacute;ch ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n) th&igrave; &#273;o&agrave;n s&#7869; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&uacute;ng l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;o&agrave;n d&#432;&#7899;i 20 kh&aacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 3 ng&agrave;y v&agrave; s&#7869; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n l&#7841;i ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh m&#7899;i ho&#7863;c ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; to&agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">C&aacute;c ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c, thanh to&aacute;n, hu&#7927; v&agrave; d&#7901;i tour: kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; 7, Ch&#7911; Nh&#7853;t.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Trong nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng nh&#432;: kh&#7911;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;o &#273;&#7897;ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, l&#361; l&#7909;t&hellip; Tu&#7923; theo t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&agrave; s&#7921; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n, an to&agrave;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ty Du L&#7883;ch s&#7869; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i nh&#432; sau: hu&#7927; ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i v&#7899;i chi ph&iacute; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham quan tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh th&igrave; Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; thanh to&aacute;n kho&#7843;n ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;y. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&#7895;i b&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a, gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; b&ecirc;n b&#7883; thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i nh&#7857;m gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&aacute;c t&#7893;n th&#7845;t g&acirc;y ra v&igrave; l&yacute; do b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng.&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh, gi&#7901; bay do l&#7895;i c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, t&agrave;u ho&#7843;, t&agrave;u thu&#7927;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m b&#7845;t k&#7923; ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;o do l&#7895;i tr&ecirc;n nh&#432;: ph&aacute;t sinh b&#7919;a &#259;n, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n di chuy&#7875;n, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n, &hellip;.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">NH&#7918;NG TH&Ocirc;NG TIN C&#7846;N THI&#7870;T KHI &#272;I TOUR</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng t&#7853;p trung l&uacute;c ..........&nbsp; t&#7841;i .........</em></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7877;.</em></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">M&#7897;t s&#7889; th&#7913; t&#7921;, chi ti&#7871;t trong ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh: gi&#7901; bay; gi&#7901; xe l&#7917;a; gi&#7901; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c, &hellip; c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7875; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a chuy&#7871;n &#273;i (th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t, giao th&ocirc;ng&hellip;).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qui &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#7853;n &amp; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n/resort: nh&#7853;n ph&ograve;ng sau 14h v&agrave; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c 12h /.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">HDV C&ocirc;ng ty th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7909; th&#7875; th&#7901;i gian v&agrave; &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m cho kh&aacute;ch v&agrave;o bu&#7893;i chi&#7873;u tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 01 ng&agrave;y.</em></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng ng&#7891;i &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; gh&#7871; - cung c&#7845;p khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; g&#7885;n nh&#7865;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Gi&#7845;y t&#7901; t&ugrave;y th&acirc;n ti&#7873;n b&#7841;c, h&agrave;nh l&yacute; t&#432; trang qu&yacute; gi&aacute;. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; gi&#7919; l&#7845;y. C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch s&#7869; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m &#273;&#7873;n b&ugrave;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n&ecirc;n mang theo 1 c&acirc;y d&ugrave; x&#7871;p che n&#7855;ng, m&#432;a. Gi&agrave;y th&#7875; thao ho&#7863;c d&eacute;p c&oacute; quai h&#7853;u &#273;&#7875; ti&#7879;n &#273;i l&#7841;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7847;n tu&acirc;n theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7901;i gian t&#7853;p trung c&#7911;a HDV, tr&aacute;nh vi&#7879;c tr&#7877; gi&#7901; h&#7865;n g&acirc;y &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chung cho c&#7843; &#273;o&agrave;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;V&igrave; l&yacute; do s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&agrave; an to&agrave;n v&#7879; sinh th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m, Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng kh&ocirc;ng mang th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m t&#7915; b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i v&agrave;o nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i th&#7913;c u&#7889;ng khi mang v&agrave;o ph&#7843;i c&oacute; s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng &yacute; c&#7911;a nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n v&agrave; b&#7883; t&iacute;nh ph&iacute; n&#7871;u c&oacute;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi r&#7901;i kh&#7887;i ch&#7895; ng&#7891;i: tr&ecirc;n xe, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, mua s&#7855;m, tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n&hellip; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n ki&#7875;m tra l&#7841;i h&agrave;nh l&yacute;, t&#432; trang c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: b&oacute;p, v&iacute;, t&uacute;i x&aacute;ch, m&aacute;y &#7843;nh, m&aacute;y quay phim, &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i&hellip; &#273;&#7873; ph&ograve;ng vi&#7879;c b&#7887; qu&ecirc;n, th&#7845;t l&#7841;c g&acirc;y thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i v&agrave; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chuy&#7871;n tham quan c&#7911;a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i trong c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7913;ng, leo tr&egrave;o &#7903; nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i kh&ocirc;ng an to&agrave;n. C&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i tr&ecirc;n t&agrave;u, &#273;&ograve;. Qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;i &#273;&uacute;ng lu&#7853;t qui &#273;&#7883;nh. Nh&#7919;ng gia &#273;&igrave;nh c&oacute; tr&#7867; em vui l&ograve;ng quan s&aacute;t v&agrave; tr&ocirc;ng gi&#7919; c&aacute;c b&eacute; c&#7849;n th&#7853;n.</li></ul></div></div></div></body></html>\n', '2020-06-25 16:23:05', '2020-06-26 00:21:02', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2 ngày 1 đêm', 'Thứ 7 hàng tuần', 'Xe Ô Tô', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`id`, `tour_id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tour_TypeTour_id`, `status`, `check_home_page`, `check_trending`, `best_seller`, `tour_date`, `date_start`, `transport`, `place_start`, `numratings`, `allstar`, `star`) VALUES
(21, '13107', 'Tour Miền Tây - Khám phá con đường xuyên rừng tràm đẹp nhất Việt Nam', 'tour-mien-tay-kham-pha-con-duong-xuyen-rung-tram-dep-nhat-viet-nam', 549000, 'upload/images/1593102862_lang-noi-tan-lap-tour-long-an-gia-re.jpg', '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><!--?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?--><!--?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?--><html><body><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-info-circle\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">&#272;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-spacing: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 773px;\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px; width: 154px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">C&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n K&#7923; Quan Th&#7871; Gi&#7899;i - L&agrave;ng N&#7893;i T&acirc;n L&#7853;p - Con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n r&#7915;ng tr&agrave;m &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">1 ng&agrave;y 0 &#273;&ecirc;m</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Ch&#7911; Nh&#7853;t h&agrave;ng tu&#7847;n</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">V&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n:</span></span></td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Xe du l&#7883;ch &#273;&#7901;i m&#7899;i</span></span></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://dulichviet.com.vn/du-lich-mien-tay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Du L&#7883;ch Mi&#7873;n T&acirc;y</span></span></a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;- H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh 1 ng&agrave;y &#273;&#432;a du kh&aacute;ch v&#7873; v&#7899;i thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n, kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; khu r&#7915;ng n&#7893;i nguy&ecirc;n sinh T&acirc;n L&#7853;p tr&ecirc;n c&ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&aacute; u&#7889;n l&#432;&#7907;n, tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng d&acirc;n d&atilde; v&agrave; th&#432;&#7903;ng th&#7913;c nh&#7919;ng m&oacute;n &#259;n &#273;&#7863;c tr&#432;ng c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n Nam B&#7897;. Kh&ocirc;ng qu&ecirc;n h&agrave;nh h&#432;&#417;ng v&#7873; Thi&#7873;n Vi&#7879;n Tr&uacute;c L&acirc;m Ch&aacute;nh Gi&aacute;c l&agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng&nbsp; thi&#7873;n vi&#7879;n l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c. Th&#432; gi&atilde;n t&#7841;i C&ocirc;ng Vi&ecirc;n&nbsp; K&#7923; Quan v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh thu nh&#7887; c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng tr&ecirc;n Th&#7871; gi&#7899;i r&#7845;t tinh t&#7871; v&agrave; d&#7877; th&#432;&#417;ng.</span></em></div><div class=\"linkMore text-right\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a id=\"xemthem\" data-id=\"13107\" data-table=\"tour\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Xem th&ecirc;m &raquo;</a></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-map-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"listDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; position: relative;\"><div class=\"day active\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 1 |</span>&nbsp;C&ocirc;ng Vi&ecirc;n K&#7923; Quan Th&#7871; Gi&#7899;i - L&agrave;ng N&#7893;i T&acirc;n L&#7853;p - Con &#272;&#432;&#7901;ng Xuy&ecirc;n R&#7915;ng Tr&agrave;m &#272;&#7865;p Nh&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam</div><div class=\"contDay\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">S&aacute;ng</span>: Xe v&agrave; H&#432;&#7899;ng D&#7851;n Vi&ecirc;n&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">C&ocirc;ng Ty Du L&#7883;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">ch Vi&#7879;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">t</span>&nbsp;&#273;&oacute;n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m h&#7865;n.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;i&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Long An,&nbsp;</span>tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&#7869; nghe thuy&#7871;t minh v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7883;a danh n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng c&#7911;a v&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7845;t Long An nh&#432; r&#432;&#7907;u &#273;&#7871; G&ograve; &#272;en, g&#7841;o n&agrave;ng th&#417;m Ch&#7907; &#272;&agrave;o, B&#7871;n L&#7913;c, &hellip;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&#7915;ng ch&acirc;n d&ugrave;ng b&#7919;a s&aacute;ng&nbsp;<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(chi ph&iacute; t&#7921; t&uacute;c)</em><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;o&agrave;n gh&eacute; th&#259;m&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Thi&#7873;n Vi&#7879;n Tr&uacute;c L&acirc;m Ch&aacute;nh Gi&aacute;c&nbsp;</span>&ndash; n&#7857;m s&acirc;u trong v&ugrave;ng tr&#361;ng c&#7911;a x&atilde; Thanh T&acirc;n, T&acirc;n Ph&#432;&#7899;c Ti&#7873;n Giang, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng thi&#7873;n vi&#7879;n l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c r&#7897;ng h&#417;n 30ha. L&agrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7899;i 4 Th&aacute;nh t&iacute;ch Ph&#7853;t gi&aacute;o c&oacute; ngu&#7891;n g&#7889;c t&#7915; &#7845;n &#272;&#7897; v&agrave; Nepal v&#7899;i 25 h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&agrave; b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7907;ng Ph&#7853;t Th&iacute;ch Ca M&acirc;u Ni &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7841;c b&#7857;ng &#273;&aacute; ng&#7885;c, tr&ecirc;n tay c&#7847;m hoa sen, cao 4.5m, n&#259;ng 30 t&#7845;n do c&aacute;c ngh&#7879; nh&acirc;n Myanmar ch&#7871; t&aacute;c.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;&#7871;n&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">L&agrave;ng N&#7893;i T&acirc;n L&#7853;p</span>&nbsp;&ndash; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m du l&#7883;ch sinh th&aacute;i m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t t&#7841;i&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Long An</span>, v&#7899;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng r&#7915;ng tr&agrave;m nguy&ecirc;n sinh v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7847;m hoa s&uacute;ng t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n phong c&#7843;nh tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7865;p. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&#7869; kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng xuy&ecirc;n r&#7915;ng tr&agrave;m, gi&#7919;a nh&#7919;ng con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7847;m hoa s&uacute;ng, &#273;&#7847;m sen khoe s&#7855;c, nh&#7919;ng b&atilde;i b&egrave;o tai chu&#7897;t xanh m&#432;&#7899;t &#273;i&#7875;m xuy&#7871;t &#273;&oacute;a rong v&agrave;ng li ti, th&#7881;nh tho&#7843;ng nghe &acirc;m thanh vui tai c&#7911;a ti&#7871;ng chim h&oacute;t &#273;&#7863;c tr&#432;ng c&#7911;a v&ugrave;ng n&agrave;y nh&#432; c&ograve;, b&igrave;m b&#7883;p, c&#7891;ng c&#7897;c,&hellip; &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&ograve;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m ng&#7855;m nh&igrave;n to&agrave;n c&#7843;nh r&#7915;ng tr&agrave;m t&#7915; tr&ecirc;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;&agrave;i quan s&aacute;t tr&ecirc;n cao ph&ograve;ng t&#7847;m m&#7855;t ra xa v&#7899;i b&#7841;t ng&agrave;n l&agrave; m&agrave;u xanh bao la hung v&#297;.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Tr&#432;a:&nbsp;</span>Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng b&#7919;a tr&#432;a<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;</span>v&#7899;i c&aacute;c &#273;&#7863;c s&#7843;n &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o c&#7911;a v&ugrave;ng n&#432;&#7899;c n&#7893;i.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;o&agrave;n ng&#7891;i xu&#7891;ng ba l&aacute; len l&#7887;i v&agrave;o r&#7915;ng tr&agrave;m, t&#7853;n h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c l&ecirc;nh &#273;&ecirc;nh tr&ecirc;n s&ocirc;ng n&#432;&#7899;c, th&#432;&#7903;ng ngo&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; y&ecirc;n b&igrave;nh n&#417;i &#273;&acirc;y.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;o&agrave;n kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh v&#7873; TP.HCM, tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng gh&eacute;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;C&ocirc;ng Vi&ecirc;n K&#7923; Quan Th&#7871; Gi&#7899;i</span>&nbsp;&ndash; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7899;i tr&#7867; &#273;&#7863;t cho l&agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m &ldquo;check-in v&agrave;ng&rdquo; v&igrave; &#7903; t&#7853;p trung nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thu nh&#7887; tinh x&#7843;o nh&#432; th&#7853;t. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&#7869; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m ch&#7909;p h&igrave;nh c&aacute;c b&#7913;c &#7843;nh r&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&#272;o&agrave;n kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh v&#7873; TP.HCM. K&#7871;t th&uacute;c chuy&#7871;n &#273;i, chia tay &#273;o&agrave;n v&agrave; h&#7865;n g&#7863;p l&#7841;i Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-paperclip\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">D&#7883;ch v&#7909; bao g&#7891;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; tour bao g&#7891;m:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Xe tham quan (xe 29 ch&#7895;, 35 ch&#7895;, 45 ch&#7895;) t&ugrave;y theo s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;ch th&#7921;c t&#7871; tr&ecirc;n chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&#258;n u&#7889;ng theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh: 1 b&#7919;a tr&#432;a, 150,000/b&#7919;a.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">V&eacute; tham quan theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh (bao g&#7891;m tham quan b&#7857;ng xu&#7891;ng ba l&aacute;).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng Vi&#7879;t vui v&#7867; nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh su&#7889;t chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">B&#7843;o hi&#7875;m v&#7899;i m&#7913;c b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a 100.00.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng: n&oacute;n du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t, n&#432;&#7899;c, kh&#259;n l&#7841;nh.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">m:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">B&#7919;a &#259;n s&aacute;ng.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Bia hay n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t trong c&aacute;c b&#7919;a &#259;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tham quan ngo&agrave;i ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, ph&#7909; ph&iacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Thu&#7871; VAT.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-sticky-note-o\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ghi ch&uacute;</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(&#272;o&agrave;n t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 20 kh&aacute;ch kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh)</em><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></u></span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; ve&#769; da&#768;nh cho tre&#777; em:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 05 tu&#7893;i: mi&#7877;n gi&aacute; tour. Cha, M&#7865; ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n &#273;i k&egrave;m t&#7921; lo c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; &#259;n, ng&#7911;, tham quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) cho b&eacute;. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 5 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i mua &frac12; v&eacute; tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 05 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 10 tu&#7893;i: 75% gi&aacute; tour. Bao g&#7891;m c&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#259;n u&#7889;ng, gh&#7871; ng&#7891;i tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng&#7911; chung v&#7899;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 5 &#273;&#7871;n d&#432;&#7899;i 10 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n Cha M&#7865; n&ecirc;n mua th&ecirc;m 1 su&#7845;t gi&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#417;n ho&#7863;c v&eacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">T&#7915; 10 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n: 100% gi&aacute; tour v&agrave; ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n nh&#432; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">&#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave; h&#7911;y v&eacute; tour:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Sau khi x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n (&iacute;t nh&#7845;t 50% ti&#7873;n c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895; v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour tr&#432;&#7899;c 10 ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Khi &#273;&#7871;n ng&agrave;y thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour, n&#7871;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&uacute;ng h&#7841;n v&agrave; &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem nh&#432; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; &yacute; hu&#7927; tour v&agrave; m&#7845;t h&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">V&eacute; M&aacute;y Bay / v&eacute; xe l&#7917;a / v&eacute; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu&#7845;t ngay sau khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, thanh to&aacute;n, x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n (h&#7885; t&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng n&#259;m sinh&hellip;) v&agrave; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n v&eacute; nh&#432; sau: Kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7893;i t&ecirc;n, ho&agrave;n v&eacute;, h&#7911;y v&eacute;, thay &#273;&#7893;i ng&agrave;y, thay &#273;&#7893;i h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ngay sau khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour n&#7871;u h&#7911;y s&#7869; b&#7883; ph&#7841;t ti&#7873;n tour:</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ngay sau khi &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c ho&#7863;c thanh to&aacute;n ho&#7863;c tr&#432;&#7899;c 15 ng&agrave;y: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 10% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 10 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 50% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 70% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y&nbsp; 05 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 100% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i C&ocirc;ng ty ho&#7863;c qua fax, email, tin nh&#7855;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng ty x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Do t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;o&agrave;n gh&eacute;p kh&aacute;ch l&#7867;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; cho &#273;&#7911; &#273;o&agrave;n (10 kh&aacute;ch ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n) th&igrave; &#273;o&agrave;n s&#7869; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&uacute;ng l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;o&agrave;n d&#432;&#7899;i 10 kh&aacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 3 ng&agrave;y v&agrave; s&#7869; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n l&#7841;i ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh m&#7899;i ho&#7863;c ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; to&agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">C&aacute;c ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c, thanh to&aacute;n, hu&#7927; v&agrave; d&#7901;i tour: kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; 7, Ch&#7911; Nh&#7853;t.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Trong nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng nh&#432;: kh&#7911;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;o &#273;&#7897;ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, l&#361; l&#7909;t&hellip; Tu&#7923; theo t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&agrave; s&#7921; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n, an to&agrave;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ty Du L&#7883;ch s&#7869; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i nh&#432; sau: hu&#7927; ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i v&#7899;i chi ph&iacute; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham quan tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh th&igrave; Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; thanh to&aacute;n kho&#7843;n ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;y. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&#7895;i b&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a, gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; b&ecirc;n b&#7883; thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i nh&#7857;m gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&aacute;c t&#7893;n th&#7845;t g&acirc;y ra v&igrave; l&yacute; do b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng.&hellip;</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh, gi&#7901; bay do l&#7895;i c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, t&agrave;u ho&#7843;, t&agrave;u thu&#7927;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m b&#7845;t k&#7923; ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;o do l&#7895;i tr&ecirc;n nh&#432;: ph&aacute;t sinh b&#7919;a &#259;n, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n di chuy&#7875;n, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n, &hellip;.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">Nh&#7919;ng th&ocirc;ng tin c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t khi &#273;i tour:</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; outline: 0px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng t&#7853;p trung l&uacute;c ..........&nbsp; t&#7841;i ......... C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7877;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">M&#7897;t s&#7889; th&#7913; t&#7921;, chi ti&#7871;t trong ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh: gi&#7901; bay; gi&#7901; xe l&#7917;a; gi&#7901; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c, &hellip; c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7875; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a chuy&#7871;n &#273;i (th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t, giao th&ocirc;ng&hellip;).</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qui &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#7853;n &amp; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n/resort: nh&#7853;n ph&ograve;ng sau 14h v&agrave; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c 12h /.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">HDV C&ocirc;ng ty th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7909; th&#7875; th&#7901;i gian v&agrave; &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m cho kh&aacute;ch v&agrave;o bu&#7893;i chi&#7873;u tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 01 ng&agrave;y.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng ng&#7891;i &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; gh&#7871; - cung c&#7845;p khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; g&#7885;n nh&#7865;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Gi&#7845;y t&#7901; t&ugrave;y th&acirc;n ti&#7873;n b&#7841;c, h&agrave;nh l&yacute; t&#432; trang qu&yacute; gi&aacute;. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; gi&#7919; l&#7845;y. C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch s&#7869; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m &#273;&#7873;n b&ugrave;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n&ecirc;n mang theo 1 c&acirc;y d&ugrave; x&#7871;p che n&#7855;ng, m&#432;a. Gi&agrave;y th&#7875; thao ho&#7863;c d&eacute;p c&oacute; quai h&#7853;u &#273;&#7875; ti&#7879;n &#273;i l&#7841;i.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7847;n tu&acirc;n theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7901;i gian t&#7853;p trung c&#7911;a HDV, tr&aacute;nh vi&#7879;c tr&#7877; gi&#7901; h&#7865;n g&acirc;y &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chung cho c&#7843; &#273;o&agrave;n.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px;\">&nbsp;V&igrave; l&yacute; do s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&agrave; an to&agrave;n v&#7879; sinh th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m, Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng kh&ocirc;ng mang th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m t&#7915; b&ecirc;n ngo&agrave;i v&agrave;o nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i th&#7913;c u&#7889;ng khi mang v&agrave;o ph&#7843;i c&oacute; s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng &yacute; c&#7911;a nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n v&agrave; b&#7883; t&iacute;nh ph&iacute; n&#7871;u c&oacute;.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi r&#7901;i kh&#7887;i ch&#7895; ng&#7891;i: tr&ecirc;n xe, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, mua s&#7855;m, tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n&hellip; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n ki&#7875;m tra l&#7841;i h&agrave;nh l&yacute;, t&#432; trang c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: b&oacute;p, v&iacute;, t&uacute;i x&aacute;ch, m&aacute;y &#7843;nh, m&aacute;y quay phim, &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i&hellip; &#273;&#7873; ph&ograve;ng vi&#7879;c b&#7887; qu&ecirc;n, th&#7845;t l&#7841;c g&acirc;y thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i v&agrave; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chuy&#7871;n tham quan c&#7911;a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i trong c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7913;ng, leo tr&egrave;o &#7903; nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i kh&ocirc;ng an to&agrave;n. C&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i tr&ecirc;n t&agrave;u, &#273;&ograve;. Qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;i &#273;&uacute;ng lu&#7853;t qui &#273;&#7883;nh. Nh&#7919;ng gia &#273;&igrave;nh c&oacute; tr&#7867; em vui l&ograve;ng quan s&aacute;t v&agrave; tr&ocirc;ng gi&#7919; c&aacute;c b&eacute; c&#7849;n th&#7853;n.</p></div></div></div></body></html>\n', '2020-06-25 16:34:22', '2020-06-26 00:21:19', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '1 ngày 0 đêm', 'Chủ Nhật hàng tuần', 'Xe Ô Tô', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`id`, `tour_id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tour_TypeTour_id`, `status`, `check_home_page`, `check_trending`, `best_seller`, `tour_date`, `date_start`, `transport`, `place_start`, `numratings`, `allstar`, `star`) VALUES
