=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><em><img alt=\"Du l&#7883;ch C&agrave; Mau\" src=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/images/bandidau/Mui-Ca-Mau.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 800px; height: 450px;\"></em></span></p></div><div class=\"linkMore text-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a id=\"xemthem\" data-id=\"14056\" data-table=\"tour\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Xem th&ecirc;m &raquo;</a></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-map-o\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"listDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; position: relative;\"><div class=\"day active\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">|</span>&nbsp;TP. HCM &ndash; C&Agrave; MAU</div><div class=\"contDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">T&#7889;i (21H00):&nbsp;</span>H&#432;&#7899;ng D&#7851;n Vi&ecirc;n &#273;&oacute;n kh&aacute;ch t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m h&#7865;n &ndash; Kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;i&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">C&agrave; Mau</span>.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 1 |</span>&nbsp;C&Agrave; MAU &ndash; N&#258;M C&#258;N &ndash; &#272;&#7844;T M&#360;I &ndash; B&#7840;C LI&Ecirc;U (&#258;n s&aacute;ng, tr&#432;a, chi&#7873;u)</div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 2 |</span>&nbsp;C&Agrave; MAU &ndash; B&#7840;C LI&Ecirc;U &ndash; S&Oacute;C TR&#258;NG &ndash; TP.HCM (&#258;n s&aacute;ng, tr&#432;a)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag3\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-paperclip\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">D&#7883;ch v&#7909; bao g&#7891;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Gi&aacute; tour bao g&#7891;m:</span></u></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Xe tham quan (xe 16 ch&#7895;, 29 ch&#7895;, 35 ch&#7895;, 45 ch&#7895;) t&ugrave;y theo s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&aacute;ch th&#7921;c t&#7871; tr&ecirc;n chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n 3 sao: Long T&#7925;, Qu&#7889;c T&#7871;, &Aacute;nh Nguy&#7879;t, Nam Ki&#7873;u,... (ho&#7863;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng) &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; ti&#7879;n nghi, 2 kh&aacute;ch/ph&ograve;ng, n&#7871;u l&#7867; ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7913; 3 ng&#7911; gh&eacute;p ph&ograve;ng 3 ho&#7863;c ph&#7909; ph&iacute; ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#258;n u&#7889;ng theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh:</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + &#258;n ph&#7909;: 2 b&#7919;a s&aacute;ng.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + &#258;n ch&iacute;nh: 3 b&#7919;a ch&iacute;nh ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n 100.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/b&#7919;a.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; tham quan theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng Vi&#7879;t vui v&#7867; nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh su&#7889;t chuy&#7871;n &#273;i.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">B&#7843;o hi&#7875;m v&#7899;i m&#7913;c b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a 100.000.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p. Kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho kh&aacute;ch t&#7915; 80 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</li></ul><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng: n&oacute;n du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t, n&#432;&#7899;c, kh&#259;n l&#7841;nh.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><u><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m:</span></u></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tham quan ngo&agrave;i ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: bia hay n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t trong c&aacute;c b&#7919;a &#259;n, &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, gi&#7863;t &#7911;i&hellip;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; b&atilde;i bi&#7875;n: d&ugrave;, v&otilde;ng, t&#7855;m n&#432;&#7899;c ng&#7885;t&hellip;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute;p treo, chi ph&iacute; c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch&#417;i,&hellip;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Thu&#7871; VAT.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag5\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-sticky-note-o\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ghi ch&uacute;</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><em>(&#272;o&agrave;n t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 20 kh&aacute;ch kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh)</em><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"></span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">G&iacute;a v&eacute; d&agrave;nh cho tr&#7867; em:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; d&#432;&#7899;i 05 tu&#7893;i: mi&#7877;n gi&aacute; tour. Cha, m&#7865; ho&#7863;c ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n &#273;i k&egrave;m t&#7921; lo c&aacute;c chi ph&iacute; &#259;n, ng&#7911;, tham quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;) cho b&eacute;. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 5 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i mua &frac12; v&eacute; tour.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 06 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 10 tu&#7893;i: 75% gi&aacute; tour. Bao g&#7891;m c&aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#259;n u&#7889;ng, gh&#7871; ng&#7891;i tr&ecirc;n xe v&agrave; ng&#7911; chung v&#7899;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh. Hai ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 5 &#273;&#7871;n d&#432;&#7899;i 12 tu&#7893;i, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n cha m&#7865; n&ecirc;n mua th&ecirc;m 1 su&#7845;t gi&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#417;n.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#7867; em t&#7915; 10 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n: 100% gi&aacute; tour v&agrave; ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n nh&#432; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&#272;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave; h&#7911;y v&eacute; tour:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Sau khi x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n (&iacute;t nh&#7845;t 50% ti&#7873;n c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895; v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour tr&#432;&#7899;c 10 ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh).</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Khi &#273;&#7871;n ng&agrave;y thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&#7911; 100% t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; ti&#7873;n tour, n&#7871;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng thanh to&aacute;n &#273;&uacute;ng h&#7841;n v&agrave; &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem nh&#432; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; &yacute; hu&#7927; tour v&agrave; m&#7845;t h&#7871;t s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c gi&#7919; ch&#7895;.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">V&eacute; M&aacute;y Bay / v&eacute; xe l&#7917;a / v&eacute; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu&#7845;t ngay sau khi qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, thanh to&aacute;n, x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n (h&#7885; t&ecirc;n, ng&agrave;y th&aacute;ng n&#259;m sinh&hellip;) v&agrave; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n v&eacute; nh&#432; sau: Kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7893;i t&ecirc;n, ho&agrave;n v&eacute;, h&#7911;y v&eacute;, thay &#273;&#7893;i ng&agrave;y, thay &#273;&#7893;i h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour n&#7871;u h&#7911;y s&#7869; b&#7883; ph&#7841;t ti&#7873;n tour:</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c ho&#7863;c thanh to&aacute;n ho&#7863;c tr&#432;&#7899;c 15 ng&agrave;y: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 10% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 10 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 50% ti&#7873;n tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 70% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">H&#7911;y&nbsp; 05 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: ph&iacute; h&#7911;y 100% ti&#7873;n tour&nbsp;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i C&ocirc;ng ty ho&#7863;c qua fax, email, tin nh&#7855;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng ty x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Do t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;o&agrave;n gh&eacute;p kh&aacute;ch l&#7867;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; cho &#273;&#7911; &#273;o&agrave;n (20 kh&aacute;ch ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n) th&igrave; &#273;o&agrave;n s&#7869; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&uacute;ng l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;o&agrave;n d&#432;&#7899;i 20 kh&aacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 3 ng&agrave;y v&agrave; s&#7869; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n l&#7841;i ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh m&#7899;i ho&#7863;c ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; to&agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">C&aacute;c ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c, thanh to&aacute;n, hu&#7927; v&agrave; d&#7901;i tour: kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; 7, Ch&#7911; Nh&#7853;t.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Trong nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng nh&#432;: kh&#7911;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;o &#273;&#7897;ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, l&#361; l&#7909;t&hellip; Tu&#7923; theo t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&agrave; s&#7921; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n, an to&agrave;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ty Du L&#7883;ch s&#7869; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i nh&#432; sau: hu&#7927; ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i v&#7899;i chi ph&iacute; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham quan tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh m&#7899;i c&oacute; ph&aacute;t sinh th&igrave; Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s&#7869; thanh to&aacute;n kho&#7843;n ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;y. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&#7895;i b&ecirc;n c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7889; g&#7855;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a, gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; b&ecirc;n b&#7883; thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i nh&#7857;m gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&aacute;c t&#7893;n th&#7845;t g&acirc;y ra v&igrave; l&yacute; do b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng.&hellip;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh, gi&#7901; bay do l&#7895;i c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, t&agrave;u ho&#7843;, t&agrave;u thu&#7927;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m b&#7845;t k&#7923; ph&aacute;t sinh n&agrave;o do l&#7895;i tr&ecirc;n nh&#432;: ph&aacute;t sinh b&#7919;a &#259;n, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n di chuy&#7875;n, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n, &hellip;.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">NH&#7918;NG TH&Ocirc;NG TIN C&#7846;N THI&#7870;T KHI &#272;I TOUR</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng t&#7853;p trung l&uacute;c ..........&nbsp; t&#7841;i ......... C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m khi Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7877;.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">M&#7897;t s&#7889; th&#7913; t&#7921;, chi ti&#7871;t trong ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh: gi&#7901; bay; gi&#7901; xe l&#7917;a; gi&#7901; t&agrave;u cao t&#7889;c, &hellip; c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7875; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#7911;a chuy&#7871;n &#273;i (th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t, giao th&ocirc;ng&hellip;).</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qui &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#7853;n &amp; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n/resort: nh&#7853;n ph&ograve;ng sau 14h v&agrave; tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c 12h ./.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">HDV C&ocirc;ng ty th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&#7909; th&#7875; th&#7901;i gian v&agrave; &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m cho kh&aacute;ch v&agrave;o bu&#7893;i chi&#7873;u tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 01 ng&agrave;y.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng ng&#7891;i &#273;&uacute;ng s&#7889; gh&#7871; - cung c&#7845;p khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng mang theo h&agrave;nh l&yacute; g&#7885;n nh&#7865;.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Gi&#7845;y t&#7901; t&ugrave;y th&acirc;n ti&#7873;n b&#7841;c, h&agrave;nh l&yacute; t&#432; trang qu&yacute; gi&aacute;. Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; gi&#7919; l&#7845;y. C&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch s&#7869; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m &#273;&#7873;n b&ugrave;.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch n&ecirc;n mang theo 01 c&acirc;y d&ugrave; x&#7871;p che n&#7855;ng, m&#432;a. Gi&#7847;y th&#7875; thao ho&#7863;c d&eacute;p c&oacute; quai h&#7853;u &#273;&#7875; ti&#7879;n &#273;i l&#7841;i.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7847;n tu&acirc;n theo qui &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7901;i gian t&#7853;p trung c&#7911;a HDV, tr&aacute;nh vi&#7879;c tr&#7877; gi&#7901; h&#7865;n g&acirc;y &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chung cho c&#7843; &#273;o&agrave;n.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi r&#7901;i kh&#7887;i ch&#7895; ng&#7891;i: tr&ecirc;n xe, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, mua s&#7855;m, tr&#7843; ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n&hellip; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n ki&#7875;m tra l&#7841;i h&agrave;nh l&yacute;, t&#432; trang c&aacute; nh&acirc;n: b&oacute;p, v&iacute;, t&uacute;i x&aacute;ch, m&aacute;y &#7843;nh, m&aacute;y quay phim, &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i&hellip; &#273;&#7873; ph&ograve;ng vi&#7879;c b&#7887; qu&ecirc;n, th&#7845;t l&#7841;c g&acirc;y thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i v&agrave; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng chuy&#7871;n tham quan c&#7911;a Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i trong c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7875;m tham quan, kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7913;ng, leo tr&egrave;o &#7903; nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i kh&ocirc;ng an to&agrave;n. C&#7849;n th&#7853;n khi &#273;i l&#7841;i tr&ecirc;n t&agrave;u, &#273;&ograve;. Qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;i &#273;&uacute;ng lu&#7853;t qui &#273;&#7883;nh. Nh&#7919;ng gia &#273;&igrave;nh c&oacute; tr&#7867; em vui l&ograve;ng quan s&aacute;t v&agrave; tr&ocirc;ng gi&#7919; c&aacute;c b&eacute; c&#7849;n th&#7853;n.</li></ul></div></div></div></body></html>\n', '2020-06-25 17:23:10', '2020-06-26 00:23:10', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, '2 ngày 2 đêm', 'Tối thứ 6 hàng tuần', 'Xe du lịch', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`id`, `tour_id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tour_TypeTour_id`, `status`, `check_home_page`, `check_trending`, `best_seller`, `tour_date`, `date_start`, `transport`, `place_start`, `numratings`, `allstar`, `star`) VALUES
(23, '15174', 'Du lịch Tam Giác Vàng Ấn Độ 5 ngày từ Sài Gòn giá tốt', 'du-lich-tam-giac-vang-an-do-5-ngay-tu-sai-gon-gia-tot', 18998998, 'upload/images/1593105926_di-du-lich-chup-hinh-cung-nguoi-minh-thuong-lang-mo-taj-mahal-du-lich-viet.jpg', '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><html><body><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-info-circle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">&#272;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"15\" cellspacing=\"15\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 773px;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px; width: 115px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh</span></span></td><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Delhi - Agra - Jaipur</span></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh</span></span></td><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">5 ng&agrave;y 4 &#273;&ecirc;m</span></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh</span></span></td><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">18/3 ; 15/4</span></span></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">V&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n</span></span></td><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\"><font color=\"#555555\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">H&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng&nbsp;Vietjet Air</span></font></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/du-lich-an-do\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Du l&#7883;ch &#7844;n &#272;&#7897;</a></span>&nbsp;c&#7843;nh s&#7855;c thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n phong ph&uacute; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng h&#7891; n&#432;&#7899;c trong xanh v&agrave; ng&#7885;n n&uacute;i h&ugrave;ng v&#297;, &#7844;n &#272;&#7897; c&ograve;n thu h&uacute;t du kh&aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh l&#7883;ch s&#7917; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n l&agrave; di s&#7843;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i.Du l&#7883;ch &#7844;n &#272;&#7897; c&ograve;n&nbsp;h&#7845;p d&#7851;n v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u c&aacute;c &#273;&#7873;n &#273;&agrave;i, di t&iacute;ch l&#7883;ch s&#7917; &#273;&#7891; s&#7897;, &#7844;n &#272;&#7897; c&ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i ta bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n b&#7903;i l&agrave; n&#417;i sinh ra Ph&#7853;t Gi&aacute;o. &#272;&#7871;n v&#7899;i c&aacute;c tour du l&#7883;ch &#7844;n &#272;&#7897; qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&#7869; c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i tham quan c&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a danh n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng c&#7911;a &#7844;n &#272;&#7897; nh&#432;: &#273;&#7891;i Gridhakut n&#417;i ph&#7853;t ng&#7891;i thi&#7873;n, Venuvan ng&ocirc;i &#273;&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7913;c vua Bimbimsara x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng d&agrave;nh cho Ph&#7853;t ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i.Qu&aacute; tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i &#273;&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o,h&atilde;y nhanh tay &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; Tour t&#7841;i&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 153);\">Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t</span></span></a>&nbsp;c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i &#273;i v&agrave; c&#7843;m nh&#7853;n, c&#7843;nh v&#7853;t n&#417;i &#273;&acirc;y nh&eacute;!</em></p><div class=\"linkMore text-right\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a id=\"xemthem\" data-id=\"15174\" data-table=\"tour\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\">Xem th&ecirc;m &raquo;</a></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-map-o\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">L&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"listDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 30px; position: relative;\"><div class=\"day active\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 1 |</span>&nbsp;TP.H&#7890; CH&Iacute; MINH &ndash; DELHI (&#258;n t&#7889;i nh&#7865; tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y bay)</div><div class=\"contDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7853;p trung t&#7841;i s&acirc;n bay T&acirc;n S&#417;n Nh&#7845;t, c&#7893;ng s&#7889; 2 &ndash; ga &#273;i qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&aacute;p chuy&#7871;n bay&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">VJ971 (19:10 -22:50 )</span>&nbsp;&#273;i Delhi. &#272;&#7871;n s&acirc;n bay qu&#7889;c t&#7871; Delhi. Xe v&agrave; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;&oacute;n &#273;o&agrave;n v&#7873; kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n ngh&#7881; &#273;&ecirc;m.</div><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"></p></div></div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 2 |</span>&nbsp;DELHI (&#258;n ba b&#7919;a)</div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 3 |</span>&nbsp;DELHI - AGRA (&#258;n ba b&#7919;a)</div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 4 |</span>&nbsp;AGRA - JAIPUR (&#258;n ba b&#7919;a)</div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 5 |</span>&nbsp;JAIPUR &ndash; DELHI &ndash; TP.HCM ( &#258;n ba b&#7919;a)</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag3\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-paperclip\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">D&#7883;ch v&#7909; bao g&#7891;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7EFA0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><u data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7F7F0\">BAO G&#7890;M</u></p><ul data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7F200\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7E9B0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">V&eacute; m&aacute;y bay kh&#7913; h&#7891;i.&nbsp;<em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A80040\">(Gi&aacute; ch&#7881; bao g&#7891;m 7kg h&agrave;nh l&yacute; x&aacute;ch tay, 20kg h&agrave;nh l&yacute; k&iacute; g&#7917;i)</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D346110\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">E-Visa nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh &#7844;n &#272;&#7897;</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7E160\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n 5* nh&#432; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh (ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n 02 ng&#432;&#7901;i/ph&ograve;ng, ph&ograve;ng ba s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&iacute; khi c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t tr&iacute; g&#7891;m 1 g&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7899;n + 1 extra bed).</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7DDD0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7E4F0\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n t&#7841;i Delhi: Radisson Dwarka ho&#7863;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7DA40\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7D6B0\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n Agra: Crystal Sarovar ho&#7863;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7D320\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7CF90\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n t&#7841;i Jaipur: Crown Plaza ho&#7863;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7CAD0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">B&#7843;o hi&#7875;m Du L&#7883;ch (210.000.000VN&#272;/ tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p). Kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho kh&aacute;ch t&#7915; 80 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7C610\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&#258;n u&#7889;ng&nbsp; theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7C740\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Xe &#273;&#432;a &#273;&oacute;n c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7875;m th&#259;m quan theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7C150\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Ph&iacute; tham quan theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7C280\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">N&#432;&#7899;c u&#7889;ng tr&ecirc;n xe 2 chai/ ng&agrave;y/ kh&aacute;ch</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D346BC0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;o&agrave;n du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t su&#7889;t tuy&#7871;n v&agrave; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n nhi&#7879;t t&igrave;nh t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7871;n</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D346830\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&agrave; t&#7863;ng c&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng ty DLV</li></ul><p data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7EAE0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><u data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D346240\">KH&Ocirc;NG BAO G&#7890;M</u></p><ul data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3464A0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D345D80\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7897; chi&#7871;u c&ograve;n h&#7841;n tr&ecirc;n 6 th&aacute;ng t&iacute;nh t&#7899;i ng&agrave;y v&#7873;.<em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7CC00\">&nbsp;N&#7871;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a th&ocirc;ng tin &#7903; ph&#7847;n b&#7883; ch&uacute;, vui l&ograve;ng b&aacute;o v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch. M&#7885;i sai s&oacute;t c&ocirc;ng ty du l&#7883;ch kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m.</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3459F0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Chi ph&iacute; c&aacute; nh&acirc;n&nbsp;<em data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D345530\">(gi&#7863;t &#7911;i v&agrave; &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i trong kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n)</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D345660\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Visa t&aacute;i nh&#7853;p Vi&#7879;t Nam cho ng&#432;&#7901;i qu&#7889;c t&#7883;ch n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i l&agrave; 35usd/kh&aacute;ch/l&#7847;n. Ri&ecirc;ng nh&#7919;ng n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c mi&#7877;n visa Vi&#7879;t Nam nh&#432;: Anh, Ph&aacute;p, &#272;&#7913;c, T&acirc;y Ban Nha, Italia, Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n, H&agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, Nauy, Ph&#7847;n Lan, &#272;an M&#7841;ch, Th&#7909;y &#272;i&#7875;n, Nga&hellip; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c mi&#7877;n visa th&igrave; c&aacute;c l&#7847;n nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh v&agrave;o Vi&#7879;t Nam ph&#7843;i c&aacute;ch nhau t&#7915; 30 ng&agrave;y tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u d&#432;&#7899;i 30 ng&agrave;y th&igrave; ph&#7843;i l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng v&#259;n t&aacute;i nh&#7853;p l&agrave; 115usd/kh&aacute;ch/l&#7847;n. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; visa Vi&#7879;t Nam nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n, kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n l&agrave;m visa t&aacute;i nh&#7853;p nh&#432;ng l&#432;u &yacute; m&#7895;i l&#7847;n nh&#7853;pc&#7843;nh kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; t&#7915; 3 &#273;&#7871;n 6 th&aacute;ng (t&ugrave;y theo visa).&nbsp;<span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3451A0\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch mang theo 2 t&#7845;m h&igrave;nh 4*6 (ph&ocirc;ng n&#7873;n tr&#7855;ng) khi &#273;i tour &#273;&#7873; l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c visa VN khi quay v&#7873; VN</span></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D344950\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D344BB0\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Ti&#7873;n b&#7891;i d&#432;&#7905;ng cho t&agrave;i x&#7871; v&agrave; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng&nbsp;</span><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D343FF0\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">900.000</span><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D344250\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A8B890\">/kh&aacute;ch/tour (Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t tr&#432;&#7899;c khi tour kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh)</em></span></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D343B50\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Xe &#273;&#432;a &#273;&oacute;n s&acirc;n bay</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag5\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-sticky-note-o\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">Ghi ch&uacute;</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A7EFA0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><u data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D343560\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">GI&Aacute; V&Eacute; TR&#7866; EM</u></p><ul data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D342850\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D342E40\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">D&#432;&#7899;i 2 tu&#7893;i: 30% gi&aacute; tour (ng&#7911; gh&eacute;p chung gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n)</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D341A10\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">T&#7915; 2 &ndash; d&#432;&#7899;i 11 tu&#7893;i: 90% gi&aacute; tour ( 1 Tr&#7867; em ng&#7911; gh&eacute;p chung gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i&nbsp; 2 ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n)</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D342130\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">T&#7915; 11 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n: t&iacute;nh b&#7857;ng gi&aacute; tour ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D341B40\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p 2 tr&#7867; em &#273;i chung v&#7899;i 2 ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng &#273;&oacute;ng ti&#7873;n 1 tr&#7867; em gi&aacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n &#273;&#7875; l&#7845;y th&ecirc;m 1 gi&#432;&#7901;ng.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ul><p data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D342980\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><u data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3408A0\">L&#431;U &Yacute;</u></p><ul data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D340D40\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D340FA0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour du l&#7883;ch, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng &#273;&#7885;c k&#7929; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh, gi&aacute; tour, c&aacute;c kho&#7843;n bao g&#7891;m c&#361;ng nh&#432; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m, c&aacute;c &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n h&#7911;y tour trong ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour m&agrave; do ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; th&igrave; Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u k&#7929; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh t&#7915; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; cho m&igrave;nh.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3402B0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui lo&#768;ng &#273;em theo Passport (ba&#777;n chi&#769;nh) v&agrave; thanh to&aacute;n 50% ti&#7873;n tour ngay khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, v&agrave; ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t ti&#7873;n tour 1 tu&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3403E0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3418E0\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch thanh to&aacute;n b&#7857;ng c&agrave; th&#7867; ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng ho&#7863;c thanh to&aacute;n qua c&#7893;ng vnpay/onepay s&#7869; ph&#7909; thu th&ecirc;m ph&iacute; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; l&agrave; 3%.</span></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33FA60\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p Q&uacute;y kh&aacute;ch b&#7883; t&#7915; ch&#7889;i visa, c&ocirc;ng ty s&#7869; ho&agrave;n l&#7841;i to&agrave;n b&#7897; ti&#7873;n tour sau khi tr&#7915; chi ph&iacute; 1.000.000vn&#273;&nbsp;<em data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33FB90\">(bao g&#7891;m chi ph&iacute; xin th&#432; m&#7901;i v&agrave; chi ph&iacute; d&#7883;ch v&#7909;)</em></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33E690\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mang 2 Qu&#7889;c t&#7883;ch ho&#7863;c Travel document vui l&ograve;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o v&#7899;i nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n b&aacute;n tour ngay th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tour v&agrave; n&#7897;p b&#7843;n g&#7889;c k&egrave;m c&aacute;c gi&#7845;y t&#7901; c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan (n&#7871;u c&oacute;).</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33ED90\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch ch&#7881; mang th&#7867; xanh (th&#7867; t&#7841;m tr&uacute; t&#7841;i n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&agrave;i) v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n h&#7897; chi&#7871;u Vi&#7879;t Nam c&ograve;n hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;&nbsp;du l&#7883;ch&nbsp;sang n&#432;&#7899;c th&#7913; ba &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33D790\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33EB30\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Do tour kh&aacute;ch l&#7867; gh&eacute;p &#273;o&agrave;n, n&#7871;u Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch t&#7921; &yacute; t&aacute;ch &#273;o&agrave;n, kh&ocirc;ng tham gia ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh c&ugrave;ng &#273;o&agrave;n Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch s&#7869; &#273;&oacute;ng ph&#7909; thu 2.000.000 VN&#272;/ kh&aacute;ch</span><span data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33E1D0\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">/ng&agrave;y</span></li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33E0A0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Do t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;o&agrave;n gh&eacute;p kh&aacute;ch l&#7867;, Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m thu nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch cho &#273;&#7911; &#273;o&agrave;n (10 kh&aacute;ch ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n) th&igrave; &#273;o&agrave;n s&#7869; kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh &#273;&uacute;ng l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh. N&#7871;u s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;o&agrave;n d&#432;&#7899;i 10 kh&aacute;ch, c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho kh&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 4 ng&agrave;y v&agrave; s&#7869; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n l&#7841;i ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh m&#7899;i, ho&#7863;c ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; l&#7841;i to&agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n cho kh&aacute;ch &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute;.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33D9F0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">N&#7871;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u &#7903; ph&ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n, vui l&ograve;ng thanh to&aacute;n th&ecirc;m ti&#7873;n ph&#7909; thu.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33D400\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng h&#417;n 75 tu&#7893;i tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n, qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; gia &#273;&igrave;nh cam k&#7871;t &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng s&#7913;c kho&#7867; &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; th&#7875; tham gia tour v&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng ty khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave; ph&#7843;i c&oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i th&acirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i 60 tu&#7893;i (&#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e) &#273;i theo.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33BC40\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Sau khi &#273;&oacute;ng ti&#7873;n, n&#7871;u qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch mu&#7889;n h&#7911;y tour, vui l&ograve;ng &#273;em CMND v&agrave; h&oacute;a &#273;&#417;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&oacute;ng ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7871;n ngay v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng C&ocirc;ng ty &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c h&#7911;y tour. C&ocirc;ng ty kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n kh&aacute;ch b&aacute;o h&#7911;y qua &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33CE10\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;&#803;c xu&#7845;t c&#7843;nh v&agrave; nh&#7853;p c&#7843;nh vi&#768; ly&#769; do ca&#769; nh&acirc;n (nh&#432; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh, th&ocirc;ng tin gi&#7845;y t&#7901; trong b&#7843;n g&#7889;c b&#7883; m&#7901;, kh&ocirc;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, passport h&#7871;t h&#7841;n, kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&uacute;ng quy &#273;&#7883;nh&hellip; ) Du Li&#803;ch Vi&ecirc;&#803;t s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m v&agrave; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n tr&#7843; ti&#7873;n tour.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33CF40\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">T&ugrave;y theo &#273;i&ecirc;&#768;u ki&ecirc;&#803;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; m&agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh tham quan, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i cho ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p, tuy nhi&ecirc;n t&ocirc;&#777;ng s&ocirc;&#769; &#273;i&ecirc;&#777;m tham quan v&acirc;&#771;n &#273;a&#777;m ba&#777;o &#273;&acirc;&#768;y &#273;u&#777;.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33C950\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">C&aacute;c chuy&#7871;n bay v&agrave; gi&#7901; bay c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i gi&#7901; ch&oacute;t, do ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o c&aacute;c h&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33CA80\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Trong nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7845;t kh&#7843; kh&aacute;ng nh&#432;: kh&#7911;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;o &#273;&#7897;ng, thi&ecirc;n tai, s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7883;ch tr&igrave;nh c&#7911;a h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng, t&agrave;u h&#7887;a, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch visa c&#7911;a LSQ&hellip; c&ocirc;ng ty Du l&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t s&#7869; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i l&#7897; tr&igrave;nh &#273;i ho&#7863;c h&#7911;y tour v&igrave; s&#7921; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n v&agrave; an to&agrave;n c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng cho nh&#7919;ng chi ph&iacute; ph&aacute;t sinh, c&#361;ng nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#273;&atilde; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n.</li><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33C360\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 18 tu&#7893;i: N&#7871;u &#273;i c&ugrave;ng b&#7889;/m&#7865; ph&#7843;i mang theo gi&#7845;y khai sinh c&oacute; d&#7845;u m&#7897;c &#273;&#7887;, n&#7871;u kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i c&ugrave;ng b&#7889;/m&#7865; ph&#7843;i mang theo gi&#7845;y &#7911;y quy&#7873;n c&oacute; x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a ch&iacute;nh quy&#7873;n &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng.</li></ul><p data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33F930\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><u data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33C5C0\">&#272;I&#7872;U KI&#7878;N H&#7910;Y TOUR</u><br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A88E20\">*C&aacute;c &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n hu&#7927; tour (&#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ng&agrave;y th&#432;&#7901;ng):<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A88BE0\">- H&#7911;y tour ngay sau khi &#272;&#7841;i S&#7913; Qu&aacute;n, L&atilde;nh S&#7921; Qu&aacute;n &#273;&atilde; c&#7845;p visa: Chi ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 100% t&#7893;ng ti&#7873;n tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A889A0\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 30 - 45 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 10% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A88760\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 16 - 29 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 30% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A88520\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 08 - 15 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 60% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"0000000015A882E0\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 04 - 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 90% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D3445E0\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 01 - 03 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 100% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D343DB0\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33B060\">-Th&#7901;i gian h&#7911;y tour &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh cho ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; b&#7843;y, ch&#7911; nh&#7853;t v&agrave; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y L&#7877; T&#7871;t.</em><br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D341570\">* C&aacute;c tour ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, t&#7871;t l&agrave; c&aacute;c tour c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian di&#7877;n ra r&#417;i v&agrave;o m&#7897;t trong c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, t&#7871;t theo qui &#273;&#7883;nh.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D341330\">C&aacute;c &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n hu&#7927; tour (&#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, T&#7871;t):&nbsp;<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D340B00\">- H&#7911;y tour ngay sau khi &#272;&#7841;i S&#7913; Qu&aacute;n, L&atilde;nh S&#7921; Qu&aacute;n &#273;&atilde; c&#7845;p visa: Chi ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 100% t&#7893;ng ti&#7873;n tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33F5C0\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 30 - 45 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 30% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33F120\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 16 - 29 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 60% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33E8F0\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 08 - 15 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 90% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33B780\">- H&#7911;y tour t&#7915; 01 - 07 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh: Ph&iacute; hu&#7927; tour l&agrave; 100% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour.<br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33AE20\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33B3F0\">-Th&#7901;i gian h&#7911;y tour &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh cho ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; b&#7843;y, ch&#7911; nh&#7853;t v&agrave; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y L&#7877; T&#7871;t.</em><br data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33A980\">* C&aacute;c tour ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, t&#7871;t l&agrave; c&aacute;c tour c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian di&#7877;n ra r&#417;i v&agrave;o m&#7897;t trong c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, t&#7871;t theo qui &#273;&#7883;nh.</p><ul data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33A720\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33A850\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><em data_liveedit_tagid=\"000000002D33D8C0\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i C&ocirc;ng ty ho&#7863;c qua fax, email v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c C&ocirc;ng ty x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</em></li></ul></div></div></div></body></html>\n', '2020-06-25 17:25:26', '2020-06-26 00:25:26', 27, 1, 0, 0, 0, '5 ngày 4 đêm', 'Liên hệ', 'Ô Tô, Máy Bay', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `tour` (`id`, `tour_id`, `name`, `slug`, `price`, `image`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `tour_TypeTour_id`, `status`, `check_home_page`, `check_trending`, `best_seller`, `tour_date`, `date_start`, `transport`, `place_start`, `numratings`, `allstar`, `star`) VALUES
(24, '15110', 'Du lịch Châu Âu - Pháp - Thụy Sĩ - Ý 8 ngày mùa Xuân từ Sài Gòn giá tốt', 'du-lich-chau-au-phap-thuy-si-y-8-ngay-mua-xuan-tu-sai-gon-gia-tot', 43990000, 'upload/images/1593106032_tour-phap-mua-thu.jpg', '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?><!--?xml encoding=\"utf-8\" ?--><html><body><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-info-circle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">&#272;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\"><em>M&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n l&agrave; m&ugrave;a giao h&ograve;a c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t tr&#7901;i, th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t &#7845;m &aacute;p, m&acirc;y tr&#7901;i l&#7891;ng l&#7897;ng. T&#7845;t c&#7843; l&agrave; s&#7921; kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7847;u cho m&#7897;t n&#259;m m&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u may m&#7855;n v&agrave; t&agrave;i l&#7897;c. Nh&#7919;ng chuy&#7871;n&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">du l&#7883;ch</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n</span>&nbsp;c&#361;ng b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng. H&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng qu&#7889;c gia &#273;&aacute;ng s&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t th&#7871; gi&#7899;i Ph&aacute;p - Th&#7909;y S&#297; - &Yacute;. Kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; nh&#7919;ng n&#7873;n v&#259;n h&oacute;a &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o s&#7869; l&agrave; tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i trong m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n n&agrave;y d&agrave;nh cho b&#7841;n<br>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;H&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng 5 sao - Turkish Airlines<br>&bull;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/du-lich-nuoc-ngoai/du-lich-phap\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Du l&#7883;ch Ph&aacute;p&nbsp;</span></a>&#273;&#7855;m m&igrave;nh v&agrave;o n&eacute;t l&atilde;ng m&#7841;n, tinh t&#7871; c&#7911;a n&#432;&#7899;c Ph&aacute;p v&#7899;i th&#7911; &#273;&ocirc; Paris hoa l&#7879; v&agrave; n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng th&#7855;ng c&#7843;nh tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i nh&#432; Th&aacute;p Eiffel, S&ocirc;ng Seine&nbsp;<br>&bull;&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://dulichviet.com.vn/du-lich-thuy-si\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); transition: all 0.3s linear 0s;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Du l&#7883;ch Th&#7909;y S&#297;</span>&nbsp;</a>tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m b&#7847;u kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; m&aacute;t m&#7867;, trong l&agrave;nh c&#7911;a c&#7843;nh s&#7855;c &#273;&#7847;y t&#432;&#417;i m&aacute;t c&#7911;a phong c&#7843;nh thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n xanh m&#432;&#7899;t &#7903; Th&#7909;y S&#7929;, &#273;&#7845;t n&#432;&#7899;c xinh &#273;&#7865;p v&#7899;i con s&ocirc;ng Limmat &amp; H&#7891; Zurich v&agrave; tham quan Ph&#7889; Augustine &ndash; Con ph&#7889; nh&#7887; h&#7865;p quanh co v&#7899;i c&aacute;c &ocirc; c&#7917;a s&#7893; nhi&#7873;u m&agrave;u s&#7855;c<br>&bull;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Du l&#7883;ch &Yacute; m&ugrave;a xu&acirc;n&nbsp;</span>th&#259;m quan nh&#7919;ng th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t &Yacute;, ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7871;n &iacute;t nh&#7845;t 1 l&#7847;n trong &#273;&#7901;i<br>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Ghe&#769; th&#259;m kinh &#273;&ocirc; th&#7901;i trang Milan<br>&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Tr&#7843;i ngh&#7879;m kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; linh thi&ecirc;ng &#7903; t&ograve;a th&aacute;ng Va