VI&#7878;T NAM (&#258;n s&aacute;ng, tr&#432;a)</div></div><div class=\"day \" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"titDay\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 700; position: relative; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 0, 128);\">NG&Agrave;Y 8 |</span>&nbsp;VI&#7878;T NAM</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"boxTour\" id=\"flag3\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Muli, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\"><span class=\"fa-paperclip\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; position: relative;\">D&#7883;ch v&#7909; bao g&#7891;m v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng bao g&#7891;m</span></div><div class=\"content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"the-content desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">GI&Aacute; TOUR BAO G&#7890;M:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">V&eacute; m&aacute;y bay ch&#7863;ng qu&#7889;c t&#7871;: Tp.HCM &ndash; Paris // Rome &ndash; Tp.HCM</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&atilde;ng h&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng d&#7921; ki&#7871;n 5*: Turkish Airlines&nbsp;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Thu&ecirc;&#769;, phu&#803; phi&#769; x&#259;ng d&acirc;&#768;u, phi&#769; an ninh, phi&#769; s&acirc;n bay phi tr&#432;&#417;&#768;ng 2 n&#432;&#417;&#769;c.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n 3 sao &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; ti&#7879;n nghi, ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n ph&ograve;ng &#273;&ocirc;i.&nbsp;</li