9;n (ng&#7911; chung gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i b&#7889; m&#7865;)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#7867; em d&#432;&#7899;i 2 tu&#7893;i: 30% gi&aacute; tour ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n (ng&#7911; chung gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i b&#7889; m&#7865;)</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 40px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\">L&#432;u &yacute;: Tr&#7867; em ng&#7911; chung gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i b&#7889; m&#7865;. M&#7895;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&egrave;m 1 tr&#7867; em, tr&#7867; em th&#7913; 2 &#273;&oacute;ng 100% &#273;&#7875; c&oacute; ti&ecirc;u chu&#7849;n gi&#432;&#7901;ng ri&ecirc;ng.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&#272;I&#7872;U KI&#7878;N HU&#7926; TOUR:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh, trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; tham d&#7921; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tour, Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch vui l&ograve;ng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho Cty Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t v&agrave; ch&#7883;u ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour nh&#432; sau: (Th&#7901;i gian h&#7911;y tour &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;nh cho ng&agrave;y l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, kh&ocirc;ng t&iacute;nh th&#7913; b&#7843;y, ch&#7911; nh&#7853;t v&agrave; c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y L&#7877; T&#7871;t)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; tour/chuy&#7875;n tour &#273;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Qu&yacute; Kh&aacute;ch th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o b&#7857;ng v&#259;n b&#7843;n g&#7917;i tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7899;i Cty Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t ho&#7863;c qua fax, email, v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Cty Du L&#7883;ch Vi&#7879;t x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n. Vi&#7879;c hu&#7927; b&#7887; b&#7857;ng &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i l&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng h&#7907;p l&#7879; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">@ &#272;&#7888;I V&#7898;I TOUR NG&Agrave;Y TH&#431;&#7900;NG:&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y ngay sau khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 30% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 30 ng&agrave;y&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 50% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 16 - 29 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 75% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 01 - 15 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 100% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y tour ngay sau khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p visa&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 100% ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">@ &#272;&#7888;I V&#7898;I TOUR NG&Agrave;Y L&#7876;, T&#7870;T:&nbsp;</span><br>(l&agrave; c&aacute;c tour c&oacute; th&#7901;i gian di&#7877;n ra r&#417;i v&agrave;o m&#7897;t trong c&aacute;c ng&agrave;y l&#7877;, t&#7871;t theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a n&#432;&#7899;c Vi&#7879;t Nam)</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y ngay sau khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 30% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh 45 ng&agrave;y&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 50% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 31 - 44 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 75% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y 01 - 30 ng&agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y kh&#7903;i h&agrave;nh&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 100% tr&ecirc;n t&#7893;ng gi&aacute; tour</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">H&#7911;y tour ngay sau khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p visa&nbsp;ph&iacute; h&#7911;y tour l&agrave; 100% ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7863;t c&#7885;c tour</li></ul></div></div></div></body></html>\n', '2020-06-25 17:26:56', '2020-06-26 00:27:12', 27, 1, 0, 0, 0, '8 ngày 7 đêm', 'Liên hệ', 'Ô Tô, Máy Bay', 'TP Hồ Chí Minh', 0, 0, 0);

